Überhellashibbycore.definition: Overly [kick ass], in a very good way. [This is a] variation of [hellashibbycore], but it sounds better with über added to it.

Über Goober.definition: Similar to [Alpha Geek] and uber geek, but specifically referring to someone who games excessively, or is focused on gaming, moreso even than other gamers around them.  The person in a gaming circle who puts the most time and effort into the game or preparing for the game, regardless of whether or not they have a life outside it, although, that is usually true to carry the title as a [compliment] and not something more derogatory.  [Generally] this refers more to people who play pen and paper RPGs or LARPs or miniatures rather than computer gamers.
Über Goober.example: You [painted] 257 miniatures in [one night]?  Truly [you are] the Über Goober.
